India to Closely Monitor Investment Flows From Mauritius, Times Reports

-- B y   R a j e s h   K u m a r   S i n g h
-- 
2011-02-15T01:21:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/india-to-closely-monitor-investment-flows-from-mauritius-times-reports.html
  India ’s government will closely
monitor foreign direct investment coming from Mauritius as
officials investigate whether Indian’s are routing unaccounted
for funds kept abroad back into the country through the island
nation, the Economic Times reported, citing a finance ministry
official it didn’t identify.  To contact the reporter on this story:
